The rare year-round waterfall, stream, and hidden valley that grace this serene property were the inspiration for many of famed author/owner Alan Cohen's bestselling books. A cozy gazebo along the stream provides the perfect space for peace, relaxation and meditation. The furnished two-story 3 bed/3 bath home w/large 2-car garage is thoughtfully placed for privacy, surrounded by a verdant lawn, large citrus trees, bananas, abundant palms, bamboo, and mature landscaping. Ocean views abound from the Master suite that encompasses a large study and sunny reading room. Two large lanais on either side of the home boast ocean & valley views with the constant soothing sound of the waterfall in the background. Comfortable open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, oak, bamboo, and tile floors, koa wainscoting, and windows at every angle bring the outdoors in. A tranquil lily pond with flowing water greets you once you are inside the bamboo gates. The caretaker's/guest suite downstairs has its own private entrance and screened in lanai. Custom outdoor shower enhanced by an accomplished artist, unique sauna, and large private jacuzzi with deck, lend to the "water theme" of this extraordinarily soothing North Shore retreat.

AWESOME HOME with Haleakala and ocean views! This 4B/3B main home with attached 1B/1B ohana has been pre-listing inspected and is ready to move in! Fresh paint in most of the interior, the home boasts beautiful Brazilian teak wood flooring, upgraded fixtures in the bathrooms, brand new Samsung French door stainless steel refrigerator, newer stainless Samsung stove & microwave and Bosch dishwasher. Matching granite counters and hickory cabinets throughout kitchen and bathrooms. Ceilings are 9' on both levels with a vaulted living room/dining areas. Exceptional neighborhood and highly desired Ke Alii Kai subdivision this is a GREAT south Maui home! Central A/C in the main house and a separate Fujitsu system for the ohana. Owned photovoltaic system for low electric bills and currently on net metering. Separate laundry room downstairs with lots of cabinets, sink and counter space. Upper and lower covered lanais make for great additional outdoor living areas. Lots of natural lighting create an open feeling. The oversized master bedroom has two closets, bath has dual sinks, tiled walk-in shower and separate tub. The home backs up to a gulch giving more space, privacy and separation from the neighbors across the way. Beautiful tropical landscaping is as nicely maintained as the home. The back yard is fenced as well. Ohana is currently tenant occupied. A short stroll to Kam I Beach, Kamalii Elementary School, shops, restaurants and conveniently located just off the Piilani Highway. A well managed family friendly neighborhood. If you want to enjoy "Living Maui Style" then don't let this one pass you by! Call for an appointment today!
